# k8s-istio-multiservice-app

A complete microservices application running on **Kubernetes** with **Istio** as the service mesh.  
This project includes a **frontend**, **backend**, and **database** service, all communicating securely within the cluster and exposed through Istioâ€™s **Ingress Gateway**.

